

locations table

id auto int
name string
lat decimal(9,6)
lon decimal(9,6)
lastUpdate datetime
freq int
service int


freq(int)

0, not checking any more
1, check once (then change to 0)
2, Standard    (hourly probably



service(int) Bit Mask
1, Weather Hourly, Daily, Alert
2, River data







Weather Current
id              int  auto
locId           int
recTime         datetime
summary         varchar(50)
precipInt       float(4,3)
precipProb      float(4,3)
precipType      varchar(5)
temp            smallint
pressure        float(5,1)
pressureTrend   char(1)
windSpeed       tinyint
windGust        tinyint
windDir         smallint
stormDist       smallint
stormDir        smallint
sky             tinyint
visibility      tinyint

